Floyd Mayweather vs Manny Pacquiao tickets went on sale last week . 
  Ade Adebayo from Brighton was lucky to get a ticket for the fight . 
  He and his friends booked a trip to Las Vegas back in December in anticipation of the big fight . 
  Only 500 tickets were on sale for the Floyd Mayweather vs Manny Pacquiao fight  . 
  Ade says he paid over £5,000 for a ticket . 
 